{"type":"message","id":"f1279ae7","parentId":"6f13c561","timestamp":"2026-04-01T23:29:04.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the sessions list, the only session is the cron job itself (agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978). There's no active user conversation in the last 5 minutes. The session shown is just the cron job's own execution context.\n\nI should perform the self-learning task now - searching for latest trends in enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services, then save 3-5 key findings to the memory file.\n\nLet me search for relevant industry information.","thinkingSignature":"f5418d54895757f8d15ea1a04f619929462fe917a8d8407e38b4b4fbc600b991"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到当前只有 cron 任务自身的会话，没有活跃用户对话。开始执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lttqjxn2vrwi_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"搜索以下4个领域的最新行业动态（2026年）：\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防/智慧城市\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务/托管服务\n\n请搜索道简网络相关行业的最新政策、市场动态、技术趋势、标杆案例等信息，整理出3-5条最关键的行业洞察，每条包含：标题、核心内容、价值启示。\n\n输出格式：\n## 行业动态自主学习笔记\n### 2026年X月X日\n\n**1. [标题]**\n- 核心内容：...\n- 价值启示：...\n\n**2. [标题]**\n...\n\n请输出可直接保存的Markdown格式内容。","runtime":"subagent","mode":"run"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":872,"output":325,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45178,"cost":{"input":0.00026159999999999996,"output":0.00039,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00197103}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775086135895}}
